You can find the related rule that causes Findbugs to report an error [here][2].

You can prevent Findbugs to report this kind of errors by creating an xml file with the following content, say `filter.xml` and running the tool with `-exclude filter.xml` option. See [filters on Findbugs][3].

    &lt;FindBugsFilter&gt;
      &lt;Match&gt;
        &lt;Bug category=&quot;PERFORMANCE&quot; /&gt;
      &lt;/Match&gt;
    &lt;/FindBugsFilter&gt;

