           .stream()
           .filter((keyCondition)-&gt;keyCondition.test(numItems,version))
           .findFirst()
           .ifPresent((e)-&gt; System.out.print(ruleMap.get(e).get()));

Since we are using `findFirst()` it is equivalent to if/else if /else if ......

